title: Hand Rolled Cigar and Smoking Cigar Bars
itunes:title: Hand Rolled Cigar and Smoking Cigar Bars
description: We're smoking the Hand Rolled Cigar & Smoking Cigar Bars. We talk with Pete Johnson from Tatuaji Cigars celebrating 10 years in the cigar business. And look into Cigar Journal Magazine and peak through as cigar-lebrities make their way up to see us for a BIG event.
